{
  "stem": "8072.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I don't remember whether my sisters had a place where to stay or not to stay.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My two sisters.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Helen and Sabina.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I left them in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I went to-- back to camp because my brothers--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Prokocim.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went back to Prokocim, which it also was about five-- five kilometers or something like that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From-- from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I went back to camp, and I found my two brothers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was Machel and David.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I told them what happened, where we were at everything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were trying to-- and they were able to get my sisters into that camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And what they were doing, they opened like a kitchen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were cooking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were-- like-- it was almost like a private enterprise.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, and they were serving lunches, you know, like soups and all kind of food.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To the-- to the-- to the people-- the workers, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they also served the-- the German-- the German informants and things like that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they didn't have to pay.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they give them the food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that's why they let them do the cooking and everything like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we stayed there for-- let's see, this was November-- till, I think, till January or February.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think it was February.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in February they started--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went back to work in the same thing by laying tracks, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think the company was Simmons or something-- a German company-- Simmons, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were laying tracks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Railroad tracks.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Railroad tracks.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
